name: UNDR1ROOF BLOCK CHAIN TOKEN
description: UNDR1ROOF TOKEN Undr1roof is a project by artists, for artists, that aims to help people who are at risk of becoming homeless. Funding is raised through donations, membership fees and last but not least, NFT sales. Goal: paying the bills to prevent foreclosure of homes and the ultimate goal: buy back homes in foreclosure to give housing to the displaced.
